Mitteilungen des Museums für Naturkunde Berlin, Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschr 52(2):251-290	tribe	Zompro, 2005	valid		The characters used for distinguishing the tribe Tuberculatocharacini are not valid. There is a (shorter than in Bathycharax granulosum) distinct area apicalis on the profemora. The tubercle on the abdomen is for sure not a generic character and could even vary within a species (see Chondrostethus woodfordi). I don´t find any character separating the species from Bathycharax.	2015-12-02T10:39:00
